ActAn Act to implement conventions between Canada and Spain, Canada and the Republic of Austria, Canada and Italy, Canada and the Republic of Korea, Canada and the Socialist Republic of Romania and Canada and the Republic of Indonesia and agreements between Canada and Malaysia, Canada and Jamaica and Canada and Barbados and a convention between Canada and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland for the avoidance of double taxation with respect to income tax
SubjectCanada-Spain ** Proclamation and Convention **
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION be issued giving notice of the ENTRY INTO FORCE on December 12, 2015 of the SUPPLEMENTARY CONVENTION, entered into on November 18, 2014 and intended to alter the CONVENTION between Canada and SPAIN for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL, entered into at Ottawa on November 23, 1976.
